Center for Computational Sciences</a>, which provided us with a graduate student
Research Assistant for the academic years 2001-2002 and 1999-2000 and has also
funded travel for presentations about our work at conferences in Maui (1999) and
Glasgow (2000).  We are also indebted to the TLG and Perseus projects.
</p>

